---
// Phase 6 Task 4-4: dashboard.html → standalone Astro page
// 원본: root dashboard.html
// 이 페이지는 SNUH Mate 메인 앱과 다른 admin/검증 도구이므로 BaseLayout 을 사용하지 않는다.
// dashboard.css 는 /dashboard.css (public), dashboard.js 는 /client/dashboard.js (public).
// nurse_admin / admin 링크는 public/ 의 정적 디렉터리를 그대로 가리킨다.
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="SNUH Mate dataset and validation dashboard">
  <title>SNUH Mate 데이터셋 검증 대시보드</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/dashboard.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="dashboard-top">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Public Validation</p>
      <h1>데이터셋 · 검증 대시보드</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">팀원 데이터, 휴가·교육 이벤트, 규칙 검증, 솔버 결과를 로그인 없이 점검합니다.</p>
    </div>
    <nav class="top-links">
      <a href="/nurse_admin/index.html">배포판</a>
      <a href="/nurse_admin/admin.html">관리자판</a>
      <a href="/admin/index.html">규정 관리</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="wayfinding-band">
    <div class="guide-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Jacob · Hick · Tesler</p>
      <h2>검증은 한 질문씩 보게 바꿨습니다</h2>
      <p>이 화면은 데이터 품질과 규칙 충돌을 찾는 곳입니다. 수정이 필요하면 관리자판으로, 최종표 확인은 배포판으로 이어집니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mode-strip" aria-label="서비스 역할 구분">
      <a class="mode-pill" href="/nurse_admin/index.html">배포 확인</a>
      <a class="mode-pill" href="/nurse_admin/admin.html">생성 · 검토 · 배포</a>
      <a class="mode-pill active" href="/dashboard/">데이터 · 규정 검증</a>
    </div>
    <div class="task-list" aria-label="이 페이지에서 답하는 질문">
      <div class="task-item">
        <strong>지금 배포해도 되는가</strong>
        <span>검증 경고와 시나리오 통과율을 먼저 봅니다.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="task-item">
        <strong>어디가 위험한가</strong>
        <span>이벤트 충돌, 편중, coverage delta를 따로 확인합니다.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="task-item">
        <strong>누가 영향받는가</strong>
        <span>멤버 매트릭스로 개인별 영향을 봅니다.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="dashboard-shell">
    <section class="team-tabs" id="teamTabs"></section>

    <section id="decisionBanner" class="decision-banner">검증 상태를 계산하는 중입니다.</section>

    <section class="surface-nav" id="surfaceNav" aria-label="검증 대시보드 목차">
      <button class="surface-tab active" type="button" data-surface="overview">요약</button>
      <button class="surface-tab" type="button" data-surface="validation">검증</button>
      <button class="surface-tab" type="button" data-surface="scenarios">시나리오</button>
      <button class="surface-tab" type="button" data-surface="members">멤버</button>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-panel" data-surface-panel="overview">
      <section class="summary-grid" id="summaryGrid"></section>

      <section class="dashboard-layout">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow">Dataset Health</p>
              <h2>헤더 요약</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="healthGrid" class="mini-grid"></div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow">Rule Coverage</p>
              <h2>규칙 커버리지</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="ruleCoverage" class="stack"></div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </section>

    <section class="dashboard-layout surface-panel" data-surface-panel="validation">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Validation</p>
            <h2>검증 결과 리스트</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="validationList" class="stack"></div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="dashboard-layout surface-panel" data-surface-panel="scenarios">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Scenario Lab</p>
            <h2>시나리오 결과</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="scenarioList" class="stack"></div>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Coverage Delta</p>
            <h2>팀 이벤트 영향</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="coverageDeltaList" class="stack"></div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="dashboard-layout surface-panel" data-surface-panel="members">
      <article class="card wide">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Member Matrix</p>
            <h2>사람별 휴가 · 교육 · 최근 야간</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="memberMatrix" class="table-shell"></div>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>

  <nav class="mobile-role-nav" aria-label="주요 화면 이동">
    <a href="/nurse_admin/index.html">배포</a>
    <a href="/nurse_admin/admin.html">관리</a>
    <a class="active" href="/dashboard/">검증</a>
    <a href="/admin/index.html">규정</a>
  </nav>

  <script type="module" src="/client/dashboard.js" is:inline></script>
</body>
</html>
